	<!-- Specific version for 11866641 -->
	
	
			<div id="group-title-1" class="hyper-related-assets">
							<h4 class="hyper-depth-stories-header">Entrepreneurs on how to build businesses</h4>
				
					
					
												<ul>
																																																								
																
																														
									
							<li class=" medium-image first-child">
		
								




	


		




<h5 class=" hyper-story-header">
	<a class="story" rel="published-1290448808152" href="/web/20101203022635/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-11797173"><img src="/web/20101203022635im_/http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/50102000/jpg/_50102143_50102140.jpg" alt="A hand holding a plastic card" />Aneace Haddad, Taggo</a>
	</h5>
								
																  <p>Fed up with a wallet stuffed with cards, Aneace Haddad consolidated multiple loyalty programmes into a single piece of plastic.</p>
